      <title>解决hexo-renderer-sass屡次安装无效的问题</title>
      <link href="/2021/08/24/%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3hexo-renderer-sass%E5%B1%A1%E6%AC%A1%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%97%A0%E6%95%88%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/"/>
      <url>/2021/08/24/%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3hexo-renderer-sass%E5%B1%A1%E6%AC%A1%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%97%A0%E6%95%88%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>&emsp;&emsp;使用Hexo的过程中，不论是输入什么指令，都反复出现如下状况：</p><pre><code>ERROR &#123;  err: Error: Node Sass does not yet support your current environment: Windows 64-bit with Unsupported runtime (93)  For more information on which environments are supported please see:  https://github.com/sass/node-sass/releases/tag/v4.14.1      at module.exports (C:\Miuh&#39;s Blog\blog\node_modules\_node-sass@4.14.1@node-sass\lib\binding.js:13:13)      at Object.&lt;anonymous&gt; (C:\Miuh&#39;s Blog\blog\node_modules\_node-sass@4.14.1@node-sass\lib\index.js:14:35)      at Module._compile (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:1101:14)      at Object.Module._extensions..js (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:1153:10)      at Module.load (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:981:32)      at Function.Module._load (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:822:12)      at Module.require (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:1005:19)      at require (node:internal/modules/cjs/helpers:94:18)      at Object.&lt;anonymous&gt; (C:\Miuh&#39;s Blog\blog\node_modules\_hexo-renderer-sass@0.4.0@hexo-renderer-sass\lib\renderer.js:3:12)      at Module._compile (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:1101:14)      at Object.Module._extensions..js (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:1153:10)      at Module.load (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:981:32)      at Function.Module._load (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:822:12)      at Module.require (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:1005:19)      at req (C:\Miuh&#39;s Blog\blog\node_modules\_hexo@5.4.0@hexo\lib\hexo\index.js:292:23)      at C:\Miuh&#39;s Blog\blog\node_modules\hexo-renderer-sass\index.js:4:20      at C:\Miuh&#39;s Blog\blog\node_modules\_hexo@5.4.0@hexo\lib\hexo\index.js:305:14      at tryCatcher (C:\Miuh&#39;s Blog\blog\node_modules\_bluebird@3.7.2@bluebird\js\release\util.js:16:23)      at Promise._settlePromiseFromHandler (C:\Miuh&#39;s Blog\blog\node_modules\_bluebird@3.7.2@bluebird\js\release\promise.js:547:31)      at Promise._settlePromise (C:\Miuh&#39;s Blog\blog\node_modules\_bluebird@3.7.2@bluebird\js\release\promise.js:604:18)      at Promise._settlePromise0 (C:\Miuh&#39;s Blog\blog\node_modules\_bluebird@3.7.2@bluebird\js\release\promise.js:649:10)      at Promise._settlePromises (C:\Miuh&#39;s Blog\blog\node_modules\_bluebird@3.7.2@bluebird\js\release\promise.js:729:18)&#125; Plugin load failed: %s hexo-renderer-sass</code></pre><p>&emsp;&emsp;屡次安装hexo-renderer-sass都毫无作用，翻了不少博客以后也并没有得出一个有效的解决方案.整个下午我就对着不断生成的这段错误提示发呆……最终在查询的过程中意外发现有人提到<a href="https://github.com/lmk123/blog/issues/28">dart-sass已经可以无缝替换node-sass</a>，抱着死马当活马医的心态试了试，在CMD中输入：<br></p><pre><code>cnpm install dart.sass</code></pre><p>然后：<br></p><pre><code>hexo clean</code></pre><p>结果：<br></p><pre><code>INFO  Validating configINFO  Deleted database.</code></pre><p>        <span class="lazyload-img-span">        <img data-src="/./%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3hexo-renderer-sass%E5%B1%A1%E6%AC%A1%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%97%A0%E6%95%88%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/Ohhhhhhhhh!.gif">              </span></p><hr>]]></content>
      
      
      
